text: Schäftlarn is a municipality in Munich in Bavaria in Germany. It consists of the villages Ebenhausen, Hohenschäftlarn, Kloster Schäftlarn, Neufahrn and Zell. The river Isar runs through it. A human settlement with the name "Schäftlarn" does not exist. ==References== Category:Munich (district)
title: Schäftlarn
